2. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure
3. Install dependencies:

```bash
{{#eq packaging "uv"}}uv sync{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "poetry"}}poetry install{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "pipenv"}}pipenv install{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "pip"}}pip install -r requirements.txt{{/eq}}
```

4. Run the application:

```bash
{{#eq packaging "uv"}}uv run python -m src.main{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "poetry"}}poetry run python -m src.main{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "pipenv"}}pipenv run python -m src.main{{/eq}}{{#eq packaging "pip"}}python -m src.main{{/eq}}

